http://www.sohu.com/a/414455128_166680	63089
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200823/b344748c77cb4fab8033a5d4e6ee1f6a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>超842亿元！上海集成电路产业投资基金二期等16个基金项目落地临港</strong></p>
